summary:
In preparation of ts7 tomorrow here's a little about me:
☆ im a qualified lawyer looking for a career change because it was...
body:
In preparation of ts7 tomorrow here’s a little about me:

☆ im a qualified lawyer looking for a career change because it was making me dead inside and life is short

☆ in my spare time i like to write novels (1 completed, 2 in progress plus a short story) and ive got an idea for a badass female empowerment dark comedy movie which I know would be incredible if done right but i have no clue how to write a script but im going to start giving it a go because i shouldn’t be afraid of failure and hard work

☆ im going to glastonbury this year for the first time since 2014 when i saw the rolling stones

☆ my sense of humour is half ultra cheesy glaringly obvious totally stupid puns and half incredibly dark dry and sarcastic hard to tell if it’s a joke off hand comments (neither of which read well on the internet hashtag excuses)

☆ i always say my favourite taylor songs are clean enchanted and last kiss but that’s only because they’re the songs I’ve cried to the most. it’s genuinely impossible to choose favourites.

☆ my boyfriend’s favourite song is new years day which is just too much for my heart

☆ i have so many theory posts about ts7 and 4.26 that i genuinely think i need help lmao

☆ all of my mutuals met taylor and then left tumblr so although im a tumblr grandma feel free to message about life at any time

tell me about yourself and how excited for 4.26 you are 💕
